results.name: Number of rim-hook (or border-strip) tableaux whose shape is the integer partition with Heinz number n.
comment: The Murnaghan-Nakayama rule uses rim-hook tableaux to expand Schur functions in terms of power-sum symmetric functions.
reference: Richard P. Stanley, Enumerative Combinatorics Volume 2, Cambridge University Press, 1999, Chapter 7.17.
